Text: I m a cook for 7 years here in chile i traveled two times to europe, but never
  been in portugal so i want to know and learn basically the traditional food of each
  region of the country,its full me of knowledge to learn  from other cultures and
  get the good practice to myself .maybe if i can made a connection whit others like
  me can be a exchange cultural of food and write the complete experience.
